  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["M", "max"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "7efe6b8b-15bc-4628-8fe5-ee44af3532e1"],
 " = 8\[Pi]) and the 2HDM necessary BFB conditions (NCL1)."
}], "UsageInputs",
